com.sebastiandine.cardcollectionmanager.container

Class AbstractBeanContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sebastiandine.cardcollectionmanager.container.AbstractBeanContainer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CardBeanContainer, EditionBeanContainer

    public abstract class AbstractBeanContainer
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstract class acts as a template for container classes, which manage CardCollectionBean implementing objects. Child classes need to implement a list of CardCollectionBean implementing objects, which represents the actual bean container. Afterwards they can use the methods defined in this abstract class on this list (assign parameter container in all methods).
    Author:
    Sebastian Dine
